{"tid":1636825,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【點止係賭王姪仔】盡責藍灣保安任義勇軍教官 與黃秋生拍《全職大盜》","createTime":"2019-10-07T23:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:05:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc1aabc53be6ba829c0e3b0027dd39abac6c1a73","tid":1636825,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T23:09:48.000Z","msg":"政府強推蒙面惡法引發市民繼續上街抗爭，前晚數十名防暴警察在小西灣藍灣半島外戒備期間，突然企圖闖入商場，並要求圍觀市民離開，但被藍灣保安上前以私人地方為由拒絕，保安好言相勸警察「唔好勞氣」，惟警員失控威嚇保安「唔好阻差辦公」，有關片段在網上瘋傳，不少網民大讚保安盡責。<br />\n事後《蘋果》發現原來該名盡責保安是賭王何鴻燊姪仔，也就是黎芷珊胞弟黎烈（Mario），早年曾是華籍英兵，也曾拍過不少電影，多是飾演警察及G4角色。<br />\n記者發現黎烈98年曾與黃秋生、吳鎮宇、伍詠薇和張堅庭等電影《全職大盜》演出，片中飾演便衣探員，是林尚武下屬。而黎烈曾是海童軍，曾於懲教署任職，及曾是香港少年領袖團中士，現為義勇軍教官，來頭甚猛，受軍訓數十年，甚麼戰機、大炮、坦克也接觸過，難怪見到一班防暴警時表現如此淡定。黎烈不時在其facebook上載穿軍服揸槍訓練照片。現轉職保安及物業管理的黎烈，昨日被《蘋果》問到網民激讚盡責時表示不便多講，只表示：「開心解決咗咪算囉。」而其胞姊黎芷珊則一直未有回覆。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191007/large/1570451383_b910.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191007%2Flarge%2F1570451383_b910.jpg&h=2718e23d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191007/large/1570449384_53d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191007%2Flarge%2F1570449384_53d9.jpg&h=cff3f715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191007/60127622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F60127622&d=wXQbzQ6sjjdDHWUhljjVfyQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=133645cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F60127622&h=4cfd635c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191007/60127622</a>"},{"pid":"83cb39f85bf29507e50745dd33d15e52dab40037","tid":1636825,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T23:14:54.000Z","msg":"唔怪得咁好身型"},{"pid":"591c2c979604dd5a737af02215c79107a98d762d","tid":1636825,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T23:48:55.000Z","msg":"猛料"},{"pid":"53cc7a8edb9bf10bcca59aa186e089c051785a52","tid":1636825,"uid":209320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T23:49:25.000Z","msg":"型！"},{"pid":"afc9ba2a5c0f326ec1e3a30a466a68e19dad9af5","tid":1636825,"uid":251936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:05:05.000Z","msg":"仲有冇人見到佢?"}]}